<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>East Bayside, Portland — Visitor Guide</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400;1,500&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --cream: #f5f0e8;
    --cream-dark: #ece6d8;
    --ink: #1a1a18;
    --navy: #1e2d3d;
    --slate: #4a5568;
    --muted: #8a8a82;
    --coral: #c4623a;
    --coral-light: #f0e0d6;
    --sage: #5a7a65;
    --sage-light: #deeae2;
    --sky: #3a6080;
    --sky-light: #daeaf5;
    --gold: #b08a3e;
    --gold-light: #f5ecd4;
    --border: rgba(26,26,24,0.1);
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.6;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 0 2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  nav::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

  .nav-brand {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    white-space: nowrap;
    padding: 14px 20px 14px 0;
    margin-right: 12px;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    display: block;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    padding: 14px 14px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: #fff; }
  .nav-links a.active { color: #fff; }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: white;
    padding: 5rem 2rem 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 60%, rgba(196,98,58,0.18) 0%, transparent 60%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 75% 30%, rgba(58,96,128,0.25) 0%, transparent 55%);
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--coral);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 8vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    max-width: 380px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .address-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    position: relative;
  }
  .address-pill strong { color: white; }
  .address-dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px;
    background: var(--coral);
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(0.7); }
  }

  /* ── MAIN LAYOUT ── */
  main {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 2rem 5rem;
  }

  /* ── SECTIONS ── */
  .section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    scroll-margin-top: 48px;
  }

  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-icon {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--navy);
  }

  .section-count {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-left: auto;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .section-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* ── CARDS ── */
  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(290px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 18px 20px 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }
  .card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(26,26,24,0.09);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .card-top {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .card-name {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--navy);
  }

  .card-meta {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .card-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 5px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 3px 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .tag-walk { background: var(--sage-light); color: var(--sage); }
  .tag-nearby { background: var(--sky-light); color: var(--sky); }
  .tag-block { background: var(--coral-light); color: var(--coral); }

  .badge-order {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    background: var(--gold-light);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 3px 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .badge-special {
    background: var(--coral-light);
    color: var(--coral);
  }

  .badge-pair {
    background: var(--sage-light);
    color: var(--sage);
  }

  .card-tip {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--slate);
    line-height: 1.6;
    flex: 1;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .card-note {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 8px;
    padding-top: 8px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── HIGHLIGHT CARD (for must-dos) ── */
  .card-highlight {
    background: var(--navy);
    border-color: transparent;
  }
  .card-highlight .card-name { color: white; }
  .card-highlight .card-meta { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); }
  .card-highlight .card-tip { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }
  .card-highlight .card-note { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .card-highlight .tag-walk { background: rgba(90,122,101,0.3); color: #8ecfa0; }
  .card-highlight .badge-order { background: rgba(176,138,62,0.25); color: #d4aa5a; }

  /* ── PAIR CALLOUT ── */
  .pair-callout {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    background: var(--sage-light);
    border: 1px solid rgba(90,122,101,0.2);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 11px 16px;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--sage);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  /* ── LEGEND ── */
  .legend {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .legend-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--slate);
  }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero { padding: 4rem 1.5rem 3rem; }
    main { padding: 2rem 1.25rem 4rem; }
    nav { padding: 0 1.25rem; }
    .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .legend { gap: 10px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-brand">Portland, ME</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#morning">☀️ Morning</a></li>
    <li><a href="#corridor">📍 Washington Ave</a></li>
    <li><a href="#lunch">🦞 Lunch</a></li>
    <li><a href="#dinner">🍽 Dinner</a></li>
    <li><a href="#drinks">🍺 Drinks</a></li>
    <li><a href="#shopping">🛍 Shopping</a></li>
    <li><a href="#outside">🌊 Outside</a></li>
    <li><a href="#wellness">🧖 Wellness</a></li>
    <li><a href="#experiences">🏺 Experiences</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<header class="hero">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">Your personal guide</div>
  <h1>East Bayside,<br><em>Portland</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Our favorite spots — most within a short walk from the apartment. Explore freely and eat well.</p>
  <div class="address-pill">
    <span class="address-dot"></span>
    You're at <strong>35 E Oxford St</strong> &nbsp;·&nbsp; Washington Ave is your backyard
  </div>
</header>

<main>

  <!-- LEGEND -->
  <div class="legend">
    <div class="legend-item"><span class="tag tag-walk">walkable</span> Easy walk from the apartment</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><span class="tag tag-block">end of your block</span> Basically outside the door</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><span class="tag tag-nearby">short drive/ride</span> Worth the trip</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><span class="badge-order">✦ order this</span> Our top pick at this spot</div>
  </div>

  <!-- MORNING -->
  <section class="section" id="morning">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-icon">☀️</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Morning — Coffee & Breakfast</h2>
      <span class="section-count">6 spots</span>
    </div>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <div class="cards">

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Forage Market</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">123 Washington Ave &nbsp;·&nbsp; 7am–1pm daily</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-walk">walkable</span>
          <span class="badge-order">✦ order this</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">Get the basic breakfast sando on a wood-fired sourdough bagel — it's the move. These bagels are special, and you can smell them from outside.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">LB Kitchen</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">255 Congress St &nbsp;·&nbsp; 8am–5pm daily</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-walk">walkable</span>
          <span class="badge-order">✦ order this</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">Healthy, feel-good spot with a huge menu. Don't skip the thick-cut bacon BLT with aioli or the bird bowl. Smoothies, teas, and coffees are all excellent.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Tandem Coffee</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">122 Anderson St &nbsp;·&nbsp; 7am–1pm (closed Sun)</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-walk">walkable</span>
          <span class="badge-order">✦ order this</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">Fresh pastries delivered from the flagship each morning. Our go-to: the malted nitro cold brew — so smooth and light, even for non-cold-brew people. Incredible chocolate chip cookie too.</div>
        <div class="card-note">Flagship on Congress has a bigger pastry selection — worth the walk on a nice day.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Luncheonette</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">147 Cumberland Ave &nbsp;·&nbsp; 11am–4pm (closed Tue–Wed)</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-walk">walkable</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">So good and so unique. A tiny, intimate space with a thoughtful rotating menu. Made fresh and with real care. Worth planning around their hours.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Coffee by Design</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">1 Diamond St &nbsp;·&nbsp; 7am–6pm daily</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-walk">walkable</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">Portland institution. Great for a classic coffee hang — nice long bar, local art, fair trade beans. Reliable backup if Tandem has a line.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Smalls</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">28 Brackett St &nbsp;·&nbsp; 8am–8pm daily</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-nearby">short drive/ride</span>
          <span class="badge-order">✦ order this</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">An all-day cafe and curated market in the West End that feels like Portland at its most itself. The breakfast sandwich is legitimately in the running for best in the city — silky egg, garlic herb feta sauce, arugula. Browse the back market for local goods, ceramics, and pantry finds while you wait.</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WASHINGTON AVE CORRIDOR -->
  <section class="section" id="corridor">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-icon">📍</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Washington Ave Corridor — Must-Dos</h2>
      <span class="section-count">3 spots</span>
    </div>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <div class="cards">

      <div class="card card-highlight">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Onggi Market & Cafe</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">131 Washington Ave &nbsp;·&nbsp; Closed Tue–Wed</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-walk">walkable</span>
          <span class="badge-order">✦ order this</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">Best matcha in Portland — full stop. Plus a curated Japanese goods market with pottery, pantry items, condiments, and seasonal finds. Get there early for the chocolate chip cookie. Go browse even if you're not hungry.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card card-highlight">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">The Shop by Island Creek Oysters</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">123 Washington Ave &nbsp;·&nbsp; Closed Tue–Wed, opens 11am</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-walk">walkable</span>
          <span class="badge-order">✦ order this</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">Incredible fresh oysters for under $2 each, prosecco on draft, and the most fun tinned fish wall you'll ever browse. Daily happy hour on weekdays. One of our absolute favorite spots in the city.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Sissle & Daughters</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">107 Washington Ave &nbsp;·&nbsp; Fri–Sat from 10am, others 11am</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-walk">walkable</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">Tiny but mighty neighborhood cheese shop and bodega. Perfect for building a wine and cheese night in. They'll point you toward exactly the right wedge.</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LUNCH -->
  <section class="section" id="lunch">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-icon">🦞</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Lunch & Quick Bites</h2>
      <span class="section-count">2 spots</span>
    </div>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <div class="cards">

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Bite into Maine</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">Various Old Port locations &nbsp;·&nbsp; Walkable</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-walk">walkable</span>
          <span class="badge-order">✦ order this</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">Your go-to stop for a lobster roll — classic, buttery, iconic Maine. Feeling adventurous? Get the lobster roll flight and try a few styles side by side. You truly cannot go wrong.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Orange Bike Brewery</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">Behind Bite into Maine &nbsp;·&nbsp; Walkable</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-walk">walkable</span>
          <span class="badge-pair" style="background:var(--sage-light);color:var(--sage);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;font-size:10.5px;font-weight:500;border-radius:100px;padding:3px 9px;letter-spacing:0.02em;">⟳ pair it</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">Tucked right behind Bite into Maine — grab your lobster roll next door and bring it in. The best gluten-free beer you'll ever have, bar none. A hidden gem that earns its spot on the must-do list.</div>
        <div class="card-note">Perfect combo: lobster roll from next door + a pint here.</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DINNER -->
  <section class="section" id="dinner">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-icon">🍽</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Dinner</h2>
      <span class="section-count">7 spots</span>
    </div>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <div class="cards">

      <div class="card card-highlight">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Magissa</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">91 Anderson St &nbsp;·&nbsp; Closed Tue–Wed, from 4:30pm</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-block">end of your block</span>
          <span class="badge-order">✦ order this</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">Greek-Lebanese right at the end of our street near the big mural. The "girl dinner" — caesar salad, fries, and dirty martini for $25 — is iconic. Everything on the menu is delicious. Can't go wrong.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card card-highlight">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Izakaya Minato</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">54 Washington Ave &nbsp;·&nbsp; Closed Mon & Sun, from 5pm</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-walk">walkable</span>
          <span class="badge-special" style="background:rgba(196,98,58,0.25);color:#e08060;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;font-size:10.5px;font-weight:500;border-radius:100px;padding:3px 9px;letter-spacing:0.02em;">★ special occasion</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">No reservations, small space, big deal. Japanese izakaya with memorable oysters — topped, dressed, one of a kind. Get there early or put your name in and grab a drink nearby. You'll talk about this meal.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Crispy Gai</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">90 Exchange St &nbsp;·&nbsp; 11am–10pm daily</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-nearby">short drive/ride</span>
          <span class="badge-order">✦ order this</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">One of our absolute favorites. Thai-inspired fried chicken in the Old Port. Get the Hat Yai wings, the homemade ranch, and the cabbage salad. Everything here is great.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Terlingua</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">40 Washington Ave &nbsp;·&nbsp; 11:30am–9pm daily</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-walk">walkable</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">Texas BBQ with a Mexican twist, right on Washington Ave. Best enjoyed with a group — get the board and go to town.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Mr. Tuna</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">83 Middle St &nbsp;·&nbsp; 11am–9pm daily</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-nearby">short drive/ride</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">Excellent sushi in the Old Port. All locally sourced, super fresh. Hand rolls are a must. Reservations recommended.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Via Vecchia</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">10 Dana St &nbsp;·&nbsp; from 4pm daily</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-nearby">short drive/ride</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">A special night out Italian — beautiful room, great pasta, buzzy atmosphere. Book ahead. Classic for a date night or celebration.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-name">Scales</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-meta">68 Commercial St &nbsp;·&nbsp; from 4:30–5pm daily</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-nearby">short drive/ride</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tip">Upscale seafood on the waterfront — one of the best restaurants in Portland. Free valet, insanely fresh fish. Book well in advance. Worth every penny for a special evening.</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DRINKS -->
  <section class="section" id="drinks">
